The company promises that these cars will appeal to buyers looking for luxury in their family cars who would not necessarily consider Ford. Although full details are yet to be released, Ford promises that Vignale customers will have their own personal concierge within the dealership, which will possibly also extend to other services such as airport check-ins and appointment management.
